    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-threshold factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted on the basis of medium model influence, corroborating analytical calculations, and the inherent constraint of the ASTM F1717 standard which prescribes a single load configuration. Overall credibility is sufficient to support use of the FEA model for regulatory submission of the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw design.",
